where $V(g(t),g_0)$ is a vector field defined globally by,
\begin{eqnarray}\label{de-turck-vect}
V(g(t),g_0):={\mathop{\rm div}\nolimits}_{g_0}g(t)-\frac{1}{2}\nabla^{g_0}{\mathop{\rm tr}\nolimits}_{g_0}g(t).
