\left(\frac{1+s}{1+t}\right)^{c(R_0)}K(x,t,y,s)&\leq&\sup_{P\left(x,t,\sqrt{\frac{t-s}{2}}\right)}\left(\frac{1+s}{1+\cdot}\right)^{c(R_0)}K(\cdot,\cdot,y,s)\\
